text: Mayachnoye () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Mayachninsky Selsoviet in Ikryaninsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 845 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 3 km south from Ikryanoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ikryaninsky District
title: Mayachnoye, Ikryaninsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
